jobDescription:
- Responsible for the daily operations, maintenance, and architecture management of the IM (Instant Messaging) system infrastructure, including messaging services, push notification services, gateways, and storage systems;
- Manage Linux server deployment, monitoring, troubleshooting, and performance optimization;
- Provide operational support for Flutter client applications, including Android/iOS build packaging, CI/CD pipelines, certificate management, and release processes;
- Manage cloud services and cloud storage solutions, including Object Storage, CDN, logging systems, backup, and disaster recovery;
- Implement and maintain containerized deployments and automated operations using Docker and Kubernetes;
- Ensure server security, access control, DDoS protection, and overall system stability;
- Build and maintain monitoring and alerting systems to ensure high availability of services;
- Collaborate with the development team to resolve production issues and improve system reliability and delivery efficiency;
- Lead the operations team and establish technical standards and operational best practices.

requirements:
