- Familiar with DevOps and CI/CD tools such as Docker, Kubernetes, Jenkins, and GitLab CI;
- Familiar with Flutter application packaging and release workflows, with understanding of Android/iOS signing mechanisms;
- Hands-on experience with at least one major cloud platform, such as AWS, Alibaba Cloud, Tencent Cloud, or Huawei Cloud;
- Familiar with Object Storage services, CDN, logging systems, and monitoring frameworks;
- Strong experience in server performance tuning, troubleshooting, and security hardening;
- Strong sense of responsibility and good teamwork/collaboration skills;
- Able to handle urgent production incidents and on-call support when necessary.

